  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libptytty</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libptytty</application> package provides a library that
      allows for OS independent and secure pty/tty and utmp/wtmp/lastlog
      handling.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

